text: @UPSHelp why send a text saying ‘call this number to re-arrange delivery’ when you can’t speak to a human and re-arranging a delivery isn’t an option? Waste of delivery driver’s time as you keep attempting to deliver while I’m at work!?
@ElaineRegan I see you are unhappy with us. Is there something we can help you with?  Please DM my team with the tracking number(s), address, and contact phone number for assistance. ^WS
